Images: ["[630_360_15301...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2018_06/thumb_files/630_360_1530179094-6389.jpg)", "[1680706430-85...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680706430-855.jpg)"]

